Package net.proteusframework.core.geo Description

Classes in this package provide geographical information.

CountryInformation provides information related to countries.
RegionInformation provides information related to regions within a country.
PENDING: com.i2rd.geo.FeatureInformation provides information for features such as continents, countries, states, provinces, lakes, forests, etc.
